= Robert Sherwood

Robert Sherwood is the coalition's sharpest public writer, turning speeches, newspapers, and radio copy into a disciplined defense of democracy and reform.

- @media_
- @faction_support_
- @kpd_cooperation
- @root: Return to main


@media_
title: Media
subtitle: Manage our party's newspapers and media.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; media_timer -= 6; last_advisor_action = 1
go-to: media


@faction_support_
title: Editorial Line
subtitle: We can change the editorial line of the party press to support a particular faction.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
